messages.text: Can you think of any reason why your husband -
He’s not my husband… Not by choice.
Well, can you think of any reason why he might of done this?
He said he would come for her…
Why?! What do you mean you left?!
This can’t come as a surprise…
But leaving… You never said you were going to leave me…
Sorry. I can’t trust you around Tasha anymore.
What in the hell does that mean?!
You better get back here!! OR I’LL-
See, that’s what I’m talking about.
It’s not safe around you anymore.
Then we’ll have to go to court.
No? There’s no getting out of this.
You can’t take her away from me..
You were too busy nose deep in work related shit!
I was working on that, I was fixing it.
And you… The love of my life.
Stop. IF you loved me, you would’ve treated me better… Us better.
Like I’m going to tell you that.
I’m not sure what has gotten into you…
But you just need to come back home.
Nope. I’ve already made my decision.
That little girl will grow up without her father!!
We’ll see what the courts say.
I swear when I get ahold of you…
How else do you expect me to act?!
What have I done to have you just leave me?
But I think what happened is we got married too fast..
I was just blindly in love..
Did they tell you to do this?!
But I think part of the reason I married you was because I wanted to rebel..
16 and pregnant and didn’t know what to do…
At first… Then you started to get more controlling..
I couldn’t go anywhere except work..
Couldn’t even take Tasha anywhere with me..
Or wear any clothing that showed skin…
Then you wouldn’t even let me leave the house!
I wanted you all to myself..
Didn’t want anyone else looking at you!!
Couldn’t talk to any other man no matter who they were!
I couldn’t even talk to my FATHER!!
Someone who then never let me leave the house.
Oh yeah… I can hate you.
How could you say that about your husband…?
You didn’t give me a chance to say goodbye to my daughter..
You would’ve never let us go.
And no matter how much you try, we will not come back.
You have no more control over me.
There’s a restraining order in there as well.
Stay the hell away from us.
Stop before you say something you’ll regret.
You can’t break up this family.
You’re going to come back and we’re going to live happily ever after.
I’ll do anything to ensure that.
If you come near us, you’re done.
Our records indicate he destroyed his phone.
I know. He kidnapped Tasha and messaged me from hers.
He’s turned off the tracking device from your daughters.
The last signal we got was from your house.
That’s where he kidnapped her from.
You left your 13 year old home alone?
I had to work OKAY! I have to provide for her now.
And he hasn’t initiated contact with you since then?
What have you done with her you bastard!
Look, I want to make amends…
We can be a happy family again…
You just have to agree to come back and love me..
Then all will be well and you can see lil’ Tash again..
She loves her daddy… But misses her mom..
You know the old cottage on Lake McBride?
Click below to see what happens next...
